<taxonomicName id="E7BE3DAE56F3C9AD02432D0678802C5E" authority="(L.) Chazelles" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="supina">
Linaria 
<normalizedToken id="013128E15FACC54F1F7152A6E083FD73" originalValue="supína" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">supina</normalizedToken>
(
<authorityName id="D02E82E04FB502FF765FC5E144705705" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">L.</authorityName>
) Chazelles
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="06E094EDA3F56D3AE6E8CCD792F532DD" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="5E41A82FEC89F0BAE1D40D0F58E61072" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Niederliegendes Leinkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="D2E2AF0B6420A27C891B22F670726941" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" type="description">
<paragraph id="44A876E3CD1EBA4018C9FA70EC1CD0FC" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="D2AA1515CAB7942D1A51A7795D452D48" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="87A0FC6BB98DD093935E9C10F7595929" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<authorityName id="4E7EEA49406FD4F5B85DBEFC5A14386B" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">L.</authorityName>
alpina
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 11) durch folgende Merkmale: Bis 15 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="B23DA5506F5B65D5AA5F151EFE5AB797" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<normalizedToken id="9EDD594947D1CCEF6F0965615A967553" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
6
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="352B3683F71303D0A0A97D7FD4A1DA26" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
15mal so lang wie breit; 
<normalizedToken id="C5D9DD02DFFEA70D4BB4841C80A5340F" originalValue="Blütenstiel" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Bluetenstiel</normalizedToken>
etwa
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="33E2061DCF700A750E3D13097D83036B" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="5162D17B5B86A301D523AA9A789D0705" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
so lang wie der Kelch, wie die 
<normalizedToken id="454814797B1B1F6F82116D63841EBD65" originalValue="Ränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Raender</normalizedToken>
der Kelchzipfel mit einzelnen ca. 0,2 mm langen 
<normalizedToken id="AB8C0D7ED84FF4AF5C8AF9D6F41801A6" originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Kelchzipfel von unten bis fast zur Spitze gleich breit; 
<emphasis id="ECD5E6B63E04D7AF6F91A58568152272" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Krone gelb</emphasis>
, der Sporn gelegentlich 
<normalizedToken id="3DBE8634C5969A18DCC3540A7FF351E9" originalValue="rötlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">roetlich</normalizedToken>
gestreift; 
<emphasis id="D119439917452403BCD0A1DCFC269590" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Sporn zylindrisch; Samen 2,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="0BE23D9124FFD0D35CBF218832B36D8F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">3 mm im Durchmesser</emphasis>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="F4C733DB449F49A68670F81AD39142DC" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="AC7BFCB773B914080A283BB6F0314C1D" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="7727E6D4DC8C6FE6EE42159F1B590154" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C2BD9B3368BCCBEB8136CF303FA766A9" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="A1045C8B4BE10BBB09959F8C7C516EE3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="5F90D421F51417BEF6BA4606F1077662" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">12:</emphasis>
Material unbekannter Herkunft (Heitz 1927), aus 
<normalizedToken id="430CF62CC405B26E44393B7BE3035FAC" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
(Van Loon et al. 1971).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EE87EA2E33435B58395C8B2C0EAC2AE0" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="AAA04DDFE6BE1C42CD3631D64A65F99C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. Lockere, ziemlich trockene, sandige oder steinige, kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="93CF9B8B32B7792DBF0E3801D85B5134" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felsschutt, trockene Rasen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B21EF70B3C92601BE23D9AD9E66D153B" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="201226B6CC55E1DB33B37D01C49924C1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Verbreitung. Westmediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
Nord- und 
<normalizedToken id="B19C07EF42B8B1340EC407314B6BBCC9" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="FF4B612EED15E23F3DF5D697C55CC2D6" originalValue="Südengland" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Suedengland</normalizedToken>
, Nordfrankreich, Westalpen, mittlerer Apennin; 
<normalizedToken id="55188DAD1DA127CBB3DCD5426F3FE298" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="C78C210E03B5D9076F5ADF184D01FA0C" originalValue="Südspanien" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Suedspanien</normalizedToken>
und Marokko. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (Maurienne), Aostatal (Calciavacca).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
